history.proof: intros a l H. induction l as [|b l' IHl]. - reflexivity. - simpl. destruct (eqA_dec a b) as [Heq | Hneq]. + exfalso. apply H. left. symmetry. apply Heq. + apply IHl. intros H'. apply H. right. apply H'.
